\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-pink-street.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"4-tram-28-to-alfama-must-do-in-lisbon\">4. Tram 28 to Alfama &#x2013; must-do in Lisbon!<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Walk back to <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"this nearby tram stop (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/dir\/Alfama,+Lisbon,+Portugal\/The+Pink+Street,+Rua+Nova+do+Carvalho,+Lisbon,+Portugal\/@38.7086951,-9.1413374,17.25z\/data=!4m14!4m13!1m5!1m1!1s0xd19347613ee43b5:0xc37964f5e5b83e8!2m2!1d-9.1303235!2d38.7124976!1m5!1m1!1s0xd1935db7faf24b7:0x1dc5a5c44783b29f!2m2!1d-9.1436411!2d38.7072119!3e3?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">this nearby tram stop<\/a> for a ride on the classic tram 28 route. These yellow trams, dating back from 1930, rolling up the hilly streets is what Lisbon&#x2019;s charm so much. A single ticket to the tram costs 3 EUR. (~ 3.5 USD)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Portugal has more to offer! Like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/monsanto-rock-village\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Monsanto, the village built on rocks.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132647\/things-to-do-lisbon-tram-28.jpg\" alt=\"tram 28 Lisbon things to do \"><\/noscript><img width=\"442\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tram 28 Lisbon things to do \" class=