=\"9-cascais\">9. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/cascais-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cascais<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/cascais-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cascais<\/a> is a tiny, charming old fishing village that is easy to reach by a 40-minute train ride from Lisbon. It is home to Lisbon&#x2019;s wealthy people who spend their weekends in their holiday homes, but luckily Cascais&#x2019;s character remains.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip.jpg\" alt=\"cascais lisbon\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"311\" alt=\"cascais lisbon\" class=\"wp-image-16086 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-300x207.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-600x414.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-450x311.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-800x553.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-1080x746.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-163x113.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-261x180.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-768x530.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-1024x707.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-1440x995.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132613\/lisbon-cascais-day-trip.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Walk the narrow cobblestone streets during the peaceful early morning when the weather is still refreshing, and streets are still empty. Cascais is a collection of picturesque little houses decorated with flowers. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Transport:<\/strong> A one-way train ticket to Cascais costs 2.25 EUR. (~ 2.50 USD)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-16088 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet.jpg 1484w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132609\/cascais-steet-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.salt