ll Cascais travel guide<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip: <\/strong>Get a gelato ice cream at the popular Gelados Santini when walking back to the train station. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach.jpg\" alt=\"cascais beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"cascais beach\" class=\"wp-image-16083 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132623\/things-to-do-lisbon-cascais-beach-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132