s-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-600x420.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-450x315.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-800x560.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-1080x757.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-163x114.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-257x180.jpg 257w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-768x538.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-1024x717.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-1440x1009.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132551\/things-to-do-lisbon-portugal-Belem-Tower.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can visit the tower on the inside and from the terrace on top. However, a limited number of visitors is allowed what means that you most likely have to queue. <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/lisbon-belem-tower\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get your tickets online<\/a>.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> The Belem tower is closed every Monday.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1841&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132555\/city-trip-lisbon-portugal.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132555\/city-trip-lisbon-portugal-18x30.jpg\" data-s