\/europe\/\" target=\"_blank\">Europe<\/a>. The subway connects the airport to the city center with a short 25-minute subway ride.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-to-lisbon\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Find flights to (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find flights to<\/a> Lisbon.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132541\/lisbon-portugal-train-station-558x810.jpg\" alt=\"lisbon portugal station rossio\"><\/noscript><img width=\"233\" height=\"338\" alt=\"lisbon portugal station rossio\" class=\"wp-image-16114 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132541\/lisbon-portugal-train-station-558x810.jpg 558w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132541\/lisbon-portugal-train-station-300x436.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132541\/lisbon-portugal-train-station-600x871.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132541\/lisbon-portugal-train-station-233x338.jpg 233w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/23132541\/lisbon-portuga